@baseUrl = http://localhost:5164

GET {{baseUrl}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###
### Login (use a real username/email + password from the `users` table)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"userNameOrEmail": "admin",
	"password": "your_password_here"
}

### Call a protected endpoint (paste token from login response)
@token = REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients?take=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Logout (client should discard token; this endpoint just confirms)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
